@node Future

  @{b}- Future -@{ub}

I can't really say that I have any future plans with Helene, the only
exception is if I discover any bugs or I come up with some new ideas for it.

The only thing that springs to mind at the moment is adding a "New Preset"
button, this is because not all people will find the method used by Helene
for creating a new WB Pattern preset file to be obvious. But I will only add
this button if enough people asks me to do it.

If you have any suggestions to functions I can add or things that can be
improved when it comes to Helene, you can send @{"me" link Author} a mail.

@endnode


